〒524-0041 {{ill|Moriyama, Shiga|ja|守山市|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, Katsube 1-chome 8-8, {{ill|Shiga Prefecture|ja|滋賀県|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft}}

